{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:24:31.597127+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: cf84c425abf7728604a3f7ff64bb4d1541abc304)", "id": "lc_b41c52f4-cbf7-43a9-82e1-715ed916ff73"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# pgdev — local PostgreSQL dev scaffold\n\nA minimal, opinionated PostgreSQL setup for local development. **Not** for\nproduction. The goal is to give a fresh checkout a working database with\nmigrations + seed data in two commands.\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Docker + docker compose v2\n\n## Quickstart\n\n```\ncp .env.example .env\ndocker compose up -d\n./scripts/apply_migrations.sh\n./scripts/seed.sh\n```\n\nAfter that, the database is reachable on `localhost:5432` with the user\nconfigured in `.env` (default `app` / `app`).\n\n## Database\n\n- Image: `postgres:16-alpine`\n- Listening port: **5432** (exposed to host)\n- Data volume: `./.pgdata` (gitignored)\n- Logging: configured in `config/postgresql.conf` (default: `log_statement = 'ddl'`)\n- Auth: configured in `config/pg_hba.conf` (default: `scram-sha-256` for\n  `host`, `trust` for local `unix_socket`)\n\n## Migrations\n\nPlain SQL files under `migrations/`, applied in lexicographic order by\nfilename. Use the `NNN_description.sql` convention starting at `001`.\n\nThe current set:\n\n| File                        | Purpose                                |\n|-----------------------------|----------------------------------------|\n| `001_create_users.sql`      | Create `users` table.                  |\n| `002_create_sessions.sql`   | Create `sessions` table, FK to users.  |\n| `003_add_session_index.sql` | Add `idx_sessions_user_id` on sessions.|\n\n## Seeds\n\nPlain SQL files under `seeds/`, applied after migrations. See `seeds/README.md`.\n\n## Operations\n\nSee [`docs/operations.md`](docs/operations.md) for resetting, backups, and\ncommon troubleshooting.\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n\n| File                            | Purpose                                              |\n|---------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|\n| `001_create_users.sql`          | Create `users` table.                                |\n| `002_create_sessions.sql`       | Create `sessions` table, FK to users.                |\n| `003_add_session_index.sql`     | Add `idx_sessions_user_id` on sessions.              |\n| `004_partition_users.sql`       | Range-partition `users` on `created_at` (monthly).   |\n", "id": "lc_4cf7f5b2-a70f-4bbb-a748-f4b884552191"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "a80a38bb-47a3-4842-aa40-c0daa57f186f", "tool_call_id": "call_00_cvcO5bbWgEE72X0KdgKr2238", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:24:31.618231+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 3b25bcaadbf40a33af1ebf5afee792282d28d196)", "id": "lc_c21e36b2-e4af-419e-afcb-0d3332072c88"}, {"type": "text", "text": "services:\n  db:\n    image: postgres:16-alpine\n    container_name: pgdev_db\n    restart: unless-stopped\n    environment:\n      POSTGRES_USER: ${POSTGRES_USER:-app}\n      POSTGRES_PASSWORD: ${POSTGRES_PASSWORD:-app}\n      POSTGRES_DB: ${POSTGRES_DB:-app}\n    ports:\n      - \"5432:5432\"\n    volumes:\n      - ./.pgdata:/var/lib/postgresql/data\n      - ./config/postgresql.conf:/etc/postgresql/postgresql.conf:ro\n      - ./config/pg_hba.conf:/etc/postgresql/pg_hba.conf:ro\n    command:\n      - postgres\n      - -c\n      - config_file=/etc/postgresql/postgresql.conf\n      - -c\n      - hba_file=/etc/postgresql/pg_hba.conf\n", "id": "lc_d7a3af33-1473-463f-a6fc-6611ebd9e723"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "a8b58b15-128e-4288-a54b-bb8187aee324", "tool_call_id": "call_01_pKpewJhjbLkVbGhS5hy93731", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
